des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the light. 
There’s no need to use the switch to adjust your home light-just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo and it’s done.

There are some simple steps you need to follow to connect your Lepro Smart products with Alexa:
(1)Download the ”Lepro+” app in the Android or iOS app market;
(2)Register a Lepro+ account in the ”Lepro+” app;
(3)You need to have some smart devices of Lepro in hand;
(4)Configure your devices in your “Lepro+” app and change the name for your devices which will be used in “Lepro+” skills;
(5)Download the Amazon ”Alexa” app from andriod, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6)Configure echo with ”Alexa” App;
(7)Search ”Lepro+” Skill from the “Alexa” app skills categories;
(8)Click Enable skill of ”Lepro+” , and you’ll be navigated to Lepro+ app;
(9) click Accpt button, you will be redirected to the success page;Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light”
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light”
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to blue”
